law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 78, sec. 36, effective January 1, 1973. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 7, sec. 2. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 147, sec. 8. -- Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 77, sec. 10. -- Amended 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 37, sec. 9. -- Created 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 94, secs. 2 and 3.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Continuance of disability payments upon death of employe.
